  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study was to determine whether 2.5 international units of oxytocin gives
      adequate uterine tone and is safe as compared to 10 international units of oxytocin following
      caesarean section delivery at Mulago hospital.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
